{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layout-post-post-tsx","path":"/post/math/number-theory/fft/","result":{"data":{"content":{"title":"快速傅里叶变换和雷德算法","description":"快速傅里叶变换和雷德算法","createAt":"April 10, 2016","updateAt":"April 10, 2016","timeToRead":"2min 39s","frontmatter2":{"aplayer":null,"wechatThumbnail":null},"toc":{"children":[{"depth":2,"identifier":"heading-小记","contents":[{"type":"text","value":"小记"}],"children":[]}]},"categories":[],"tags":["acm","大数乘法","快速傅里叶变换"],"ast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"这是一篇旧文，当时采用 tex 编写的，仅将其编译成的 "},{"type":"linkReference","identifier":"doc-pdf","label":"doc-pdf","referenceType":"full","children":[{"type":"text","value":"PDF 挂在此处"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小记"}],"identifier":"heading-小记"},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"说起来，实在要感谢 lyl 学长（可能他并不想我写上他的名字，以下以他常用的名字\nSparklingWind 指代）。大一的时候看了 SparklingWind 的《高中生学 FFT 算法》，当时自己实在太弱（虽然现在还是弱。。）以至于看得云里雾里。后来 SparklingWind 教我用 LaTeX，实在是让我受益匪浅。LaTeX 是一款精致的排版系统，可以漂亮、准确的表达出你心中所想。于是，我决定要基于自己的理解用 LaTeX 写一份 FFT 的学习笔记云云的东西，我把它命令为 SomethingAboutFFT\n"},{"type":"footnote","children":[{"type":"text","value":"2021-06-12T13:53:22.823Z 整理旧文时，更名为"},{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","value":"快速傅里叶变换和雷德算法"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"，初衷是担心 LaTeX 这种软件对中文名不友好。。。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"当时写了一份类似注解一样的东西，好像有 7 页，但是代码十分恶心。。之后随着对 LaTeX 学习的深入，又几经修改。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"直到 2015 年暑假的一天晚上突然来了灵感把 "},{"type":"linkReference","identifier":"hnu-10004-problem","label":"hnu-10004-problem","referenceType":"full","children":[{"type":"text","value":"HNU10004"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 给过了\n"},{"type":"footnote","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Accepted 的源码见 "},{"type":"linkReference","identifier":"hnu-10004-solution","label":"hnu-10004-solution","referenceType":"full","children":[{"type":"text","value":"此处"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"，心情大好，决定重写这份文档。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"真的很用心的去完成它，希望你能喜欢。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"这是一篇旧文，当时采用 tex 编写的，Markdown 不能完全识别 LaTeX 代码，所以谨附上其编译成的 "},{"type":"linkReference","identifier":"doc-pdf","label":"doc-pdf","referenceType":"full","children":[{"type":"text","value":"PDF"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，以纪念这段寻常的往事。"}]}]},"ecmaImports":[],"definitionMap":{"doc-pdf":{"type":"definition","identifier":"doc-pdf","label":"doc-pdf","url":"/static/47c244fbb3bfe287fc13a98ba1d4ab87fdb564e3/fft.pdf"},"hnu-10004-problem":{"type":"definition","identifier":"hnu-10004-problem","label":"hnu-10004-problem","url":"http://acm.hnu.cn/online/?action=problem&type=show&id=10004&courseid=0"},"hnu-10004-solution":{"type":"definition","identifier":"hnu-10004-solution","label":"hnu-10004-solution","url":"/static/b21ab483c0dba0c580d364e4c4c4fcb27b592561/hnu-10004.cpp"}},"footnoteDefinitionMap":{"footnote-1":{"type":"footnoteDefinition","identifier":"footnote-1","label":"1","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"2021-06-12T13:53:22.823Z 整理旧文时，更名为"},{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","value":"快速傅里叶变换和雷德算法"}]}]}]},"footnote-2":{"type":"footnoteDefinition","identifier":"footnote-2","label":"2","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Accepted 的源码见 "},{"type":"linkReference","identifier":"hnu-10004-solution","label":"hnu-10004-solution","referenceType":"full","children":[{"type":"text","value":"此处"}]}]}]}},"fields":{"slug":"/post/math/number-theory/fft/"}},"previous":{"title":"HDU-5306 Gorgeous Sequence 解题报告","fields":{"slug":"/post/acm/oj/hdu/5306/"}},"next":{"title":"HDU-5574 Colorful Tree 解题报告（原 2015-上海区域赛-C）","fields":{"slug":"/post/acm/oj/hdu/5574/"}},"postItems":{"nodes":[{"title":"最长公共子序列（LCS）","createAt":"2021-06-02","tags":["最长公共子序列","LCS"],"fields":{"slug":"/post/algorithm/LCS/"}},{"title":"最长上升子序列（LIS）","cr